    {
      "name": "TemplateVaultState",
      "docs": [
        "Per-vault state account for this adapter.",
        "",
        "Each vault instance stores:",
        "- Authority and mint metadata",
        "- Total underlying tokens and shares in the vault",
        "- Protocol tracking for CPI routing",
        "- Operational status (Active / Paused / Deprecated)",
        "",
        "### Customizing for your protocol",
        "Add protocol-specific fields here, for example:",
        "- `pool_id: Pubkey` — which pool/lending-market this vault targets",
        "- `strategy_id: u64` — which strategy variant to use",
        "- `reserve_index: u16` — which reserve in a multi-reserve protocol",
        "",
        "Fields you may remove if not needed:",
        "- `protocol_program_id` — if your adapter has no external CPI (like Maple w/ syrupUSDC)",
        "- `last_yield_sync_ts` — if your protocol doesn't need periodic yield sync"
      ],
      "type": {
        "kind": "struct",
        "fields": [
          {
            "name": "authority",
            "type": "pubkey"
          },
          {
            "name": "underlying_mint",
            "type": "pubkey"
          },
          {
            "name": "total_underlying",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "total_shares",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "protocol_program_id",
            "type": "pubkey"
          },
          {
            "name": "protocol_routed_underlying",
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "last_yield_sync_ts",
            "type": "i64"
          },
          {
            "name": "status",
            "type": {
              "defined": {
                "name": "VaultStatus"
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "bump",
            "type": "u8"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "VaultStatus",
      "docs": [
        "Operational status of an adapter vault.",
        "",
        "- `Active` — deposits and withdrawals are allowed.",
        "- `DepositsPaused` — deposits blocked, withdrawals still allowed.",
        "- `Paused` — deposits and withdrawals are blocked; config remains intact.",
        "- `Deprecated` — vault is permanently retired; no operations allowed.",
        "",
        "# Serialization order",
        "`DepositsPaused` is appended **after** `Deprecated` so that the Borsh",
        "discriminants of the original three variants (`Active` = 0, `Paused` = 1,",
        "`Deprecated` = 2) remain unchanged — preserving backward compatibility",
        "with all existing on-chain vault accounts."
      ],
      "repr": {
        "kind": "rust"
      },
      "type": {
        "kind": "enum",
        "variants": [
          {
            "name": "Active"
          },
          {
            "name": "Paused"
          },
          {
            "name": "Deprecated"
          },
          {
            "name": "DepositsPaused"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
